  ('medical-tech-moex-19968', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '因門脈高血壓（portal hypertension）發生併發症而致死的主要病因是： 腹水  食道靜脈曲張  脾腫大  痔瘡', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 59, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-19969', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '先天性巨大結腸症的原因是因腸道： 先天性平滑肌肥厚  先天性血管阻塞缺氧  先天性缺乏神經節細胞  先天性細胞增生', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 60, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-19970', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '發生肝細胞大塊壞死（massive necrosis）的肝炎是： 猛爆性肝炎（fulminant hepatitis）  輸血後肝炎（post-transfusion hepatitis） 黃疸性急性肝炎（icteric acute hepatitis）  慢性肝炎（chronic hepatitis）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 61, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-19971', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於急性胰臟炎的敘述，請選出正確者： 血中澱粉酵素（amylase）上升   胰臟管道纖維化   造成脂 肪壞死   急性胰臟炎是胰臟癌發生前因', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 62, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-19972', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不屬於淋巴系統的反應性淋巴腺病變（reactive lymphadenopathy）： 淋巴瘤（lymphoma）    肉芽腫發炎（granulomatous inflammation） 濾泡增生（follicular hyperplasia）  急性淋巴腺炎（acute lymphadenitis）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 63, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-19973', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列為有關血球的疾病，何者正確？ 鐮刀細胞型貧血（sickle cell anemia）是缺乏血紅素α球蛋白（α-globin）鏈所致 海洋性貧血（thalassemia）是血紅素球蛋白（globin）鏈合成缺損所致 葡萄糖-6-磷酸鹽去氫 （Glucose-6-phosphate dehydrogenase）缺乏症血管脆弱易出血 飲食中鐵質不足會造成血鐵素症（hemosiderosis）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 64, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-19974', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者與幽門桿菌Helicobacter pylori感染有密切關連： 多發性骨髓瘤（multiple myeloma）  胃之黏膜淋巴組織淋巴瘤（MALT lymphoma） 何杰金氏（Hodgkin）淋巴瘤  成人T細胞淋巴瘤（adult T-cell lymphoma）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 65, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-19975', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為腎小球腎炎的主要發生機制？ 細菌感染  毒素的破壞作用  免疫反應  新陳代謝異常', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 66, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-19976', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '因低血壓及休克而引起的急性腎功能衰竭之主要變化是： 腎臟梗塞（infarction）    急性腎盂腎炎（acute pyelonephritis） 急性腎小球腎炎（acute glomerulonephritis）  急性腎小管壞死（acute tubular necrosis）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 67, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-19977', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '病人於服藥10天後突然發燒，皮膚出疹及腎衰竭，最可能的病變是： 急性腎盂腎炎（acute pyelonephritis）  急性腎小球腎炎（acute glomerulonephritis） 急性腎小管壞死（acute tubular necrosis）  急性間質性腎炎（acute interstitial nephritis）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:13+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8e438fc0348b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a94d98be0292", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 68, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
